	<content><![CDATA[const hide = (...el) => [...el].forEach(e => (e.style.display = 'none'));]]></content>
	<description>Hides all the elements specified.  Use the spread operator (`...`) and `Array.forEach()` to apply `display: none` to each element specified.</description>
